  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Taglib</title>

    <para>Installez <application>Taglib</application> en lançant les commandes
    suivantes </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd build &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr \
      -DWITH_MP4=ON \
      -DWITH_ASF=ON \
    .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="commands">
    <title>Explications des commandes</title>

    <para><option>-DWITH_MP4=ON</option>&nbsp;: Enables support for MP4/M4A tags.</para>
    <para><option>-DWITH_ASF=ON</option>&nbsp;: Enables support for WMA tags.</para>

  </sect2>

